title: The Most Talented People At The Edinburgh Fringe | StreetSmart
description: In this Max Fosh video, he sets out to find the most talented people at the Edinburgh Fringe festival.
summary: Max Fosh searches for the most talented people at the Edinburgh Fringe festival, showcasing their unique skills and performances.
payoff: The humor in this video comes from the diverse range of talents and performances that Max encounters, from beatboxers to contortionists, showcasing the creativity and skills of the performers at the festival.
